Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.09,0:00:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
