Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.99,0:01:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是你做过最好的舒芙蕾蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is the best soufflé you have ever created
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:06.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1201,908)}亲亲章鱼
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.87,0:01:08.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:08.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, chef
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.03,0:01:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.23,0:02:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你是我在这附近最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're my best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the whole neighborhood
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你是最笨的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you are the dumbest idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认识你就是我的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it has ever been my misfortune to know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的这么觉得吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有眼睛的都能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone with eyes could see that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  我觉得你很丑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I think you're ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄色丑得很
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yellow is ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我再也不想认识你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I no longer wish to know you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你玷污了海底居民这个名号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You give bottom dwellers a bad name
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡你每无脑一次我都能赚一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I had a dollar for every brain you don't have
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我还真赚到这块钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd have one dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.89,0:03:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我听说宠物店那边有份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, I heard there was a job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,opening down at the pet shop
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以当垫屁股用的报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as some newspaper
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这话显得你像个大笨蛋  你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That makes you a big dummy, you dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是是是  这就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, that means that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.90,0:03:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也一样笨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so are you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  你就是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, you're a turkey
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's what you are
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就是更大的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a bigger one
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是黄色的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you're still yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道还有什么东西是黄色的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what else is yellow?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.37,0:03:52.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:52.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我也不稀罕你怎么叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter what you call me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我再也不想看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause I never want to see you again anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你噎着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're choking
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我得先去洗个手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I should wash my hands first
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You saved me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.29,0:05:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.25,0:05:14.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:14.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是个救命恩人  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a real lifesaver, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're friends
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just friends
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们今晚要做什么呢  最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what are we going to do tonight, best friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.52,0:05:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要练我的竖笛独奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I was going to practice my clarinet solo
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clarinet?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love music
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁需要他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs them?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正他们也没意思  对吧小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're no fun anyway, right, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥将要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward will be performing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.91,0:05:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己改编的e小调独奏曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his version of "Solitude in E Minor"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.91,0:05:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,e小调  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"E minor", all right, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在担心什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I worried about?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我朋友多得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got plenty of friends
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以一口气说出三个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can name three right off the bat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The gang's all here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我闪到腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I threw out my back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑住  我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.05,0:06:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.89,0:06:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.35,0:07:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel great
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个真正的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a real friend
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.07,0:07:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  章鱼哥兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squiddy old pal
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友之间就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what friends are for
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋派大星在你家睡着了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So dumb Patrick fell asleep on you, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.62,0:07:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某些朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some friend
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正的朋友会为你演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A real friend would perform for you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来吹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You play?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多年以来都在拉童车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been playing bassinet for years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.34,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 低音提琴为double bass\N此处"bassinet"为误称 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个A音  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me an A buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.47,0:07:38.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥是我全世界最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:38.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is my best friend in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.48,0:07:44.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥是我全海洋最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:44.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is my best friend in the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidwar--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比起海绵宝宝更喜欢派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Likes Patrick More than SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星是个脏又臭的烂朋友  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick is a dirty, stinky, rotten friend, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can fix this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天再见了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打我电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Call me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想把自己擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel like I need to scrub myself
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  我帮你预热了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, I warmed it up for you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, get out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And put some clothes on
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  章鱼哥大兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Squidward, old buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然发现了这种肮脏勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So this is what I find, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友和前任最好的朋友还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My best friend and my ex-best friend and
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一堆橡皮浴缸玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rubber bath toys
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.12,0:08:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.12,0:08:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可是我朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he was my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会碰上这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening to me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.13,0:08:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要有个计划来让那两个和好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a plan to get those two back together
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后不再烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and out of my hair
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dinner party?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想念我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look stunning
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁愿跟你一块吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd much rather dine with you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不跟那个垃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than that lousy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, what gives?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不跟那个疯子坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sitting near that maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, neither
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was a setup
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个不是我最好的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you two were my best friends
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是你最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am your best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要不要来点苏打水  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how about some soda, guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, please
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要给你最好的朋友来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some for your best friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在能来点了吗  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have some now, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.53,0:09:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要苏打水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need some more
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没喝到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still didn't get any
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More, please
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.37,0:10:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.08,0:10:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
