Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两位抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苏打水都喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all out of pop
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去再装一点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go get some more
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你们就先在这聊会天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just stay here and chat?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该马上走开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should just walk away right now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是惊喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我请他们过来  让他俩单独待我家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I invited them in and I left them alone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  今天学到了什么教训
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Squidward, what have we learned today?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟海绵宝宝又是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and SpongeBob are friends again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚别处交友去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go be friends somewhere else
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不想要我们帮你清理一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want us to help you clean this up a little?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他应该是嫉妒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think he's jealous
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How pathetic
