Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾考就是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The big boating exam is today
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没觉得这么有能力过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never felt so capable
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.11,0:12:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好搬走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready to move?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是准备好去过驾考了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm ready to pass my boating test
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:55.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(795,294)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready-eady
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  我再也用不着你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, pal, I won't be needing you anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚考到驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just got my license
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等下也要考到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting mine next
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不见得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doubt it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马路上见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you on the road
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.81,0:13:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我要过驾考的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today is the day I'm going to pass my boating exam
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就考考看  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先必须
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First we must--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先必须通过科目一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First I must pass the oral exam
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对我能力有信心  绝对能成功通过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am confident in my ability to successfully succeed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  第一题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, number one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船的前部是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the front of the boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bow
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后部是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the back?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.13,0:13:47.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:47.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stern
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三题  右侧是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number three, right is--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,右舷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Starboard
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.39,0:13:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,左舷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,port
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,skipper
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.10,0:13:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,deck
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.35,0:13:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.60,0:13:51.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:51.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,galley
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,龙骨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,keel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1924
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1924
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你通过科目一了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've passed the oral test
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太惊喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.77,0:14:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你又要参加科目二了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to once again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take the driving portion of the exam
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这艘船  就这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In this boat, right here?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it time already?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上船  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in the boat, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  要上船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, absolutely
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在要做的就是上路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is get on the track
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.75,0:14:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先你应该要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the first thing you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1924
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1924?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先应该要把船发动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First thing is to start the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, relax
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是艘船而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  那接下来要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, now, what do you do next?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.15,0:14:40.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油门踩到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:40.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floor it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.31,0:14:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  不要踩油门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't floor it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.11,0:14:43.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油门踩到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:43.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floor it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, don't
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踩油门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,floor it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  油门踩到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, floor it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踩到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floor it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(627,610)}半壳
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.20,0:14:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道这是为什么  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我挂驾考已经挂烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of failing that boating test
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经都考了37次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've already taken it 37 times
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1193,942)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  38次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, 38
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝不步行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not walking
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海星突击队员  完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is star ranger, over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.77,0:15:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有份惊喜要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a surprise for you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我没这个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Patrick, I'm not in the mood
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of bed
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.20,0:15:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你壁橱那儿准备惊喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to your closet for a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我到壁橱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm at the closet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仔细听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西又粉又方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's pink and square at the same time?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, don't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在烦心得很
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got too much to worry about
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我过不了驾考
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't pass my boating exam
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经考了37
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've taken it 37--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,38次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,38 times
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还知道所有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know all the answers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果一上船就全忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until I get behind the wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要有样东西让我思路清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just need something to help me think straight
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我思路就清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thinking straight is what I do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来开船  我来帮你想答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You drive, and I'll do all the thinking for you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要怎样才能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we going to do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请回答  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.29,0:16:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能从脑袋里听见你声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can hear you in my head
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我驾考的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While I'm taking the test
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以告诉我所有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can give me all the answers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑门上伸出个天线会不会显得我很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't I look silly with this antenna
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming out of my head?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星呼叫海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat to Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星呼叫海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat to Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,测试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Testing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,测试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Testing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.48,0:16:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,测试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Testing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,测  测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Test, test
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you read?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵呼叫海星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge to Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已清晰响亮收到  完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I read you loud and clear, over
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好苹果了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got your apple ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸运内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky undergarments?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:06.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(797,652)}幸运
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内裤  苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Underwear, apple
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经做好考到驾照的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ready to get that license
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现自然点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Act natural
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把苹果给她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give her the apple
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶快这事过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先你应该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the first thing you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把船发动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
